'''Rare Animals''' can only be obtained from existing offers in the Trading Post or when Trading a common animal, whereas '''Common Animals''' are obtainable by both posting an ad on the Trading Post and existing offers in the Trading Post.

===Animal Hats===
Some animals may unlock an animal hat with the purchase of an animal. These animal hats are collectible [[accessories]] that your character and NPCs may equip under the Main Menu. There are a total of 13 animal caps and obtaining all caps unlocks the Cap-ybara [[Achievements|achievement]].

